        "rich_text_ccxpK9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Saying “yes” is more than a moment, it’s the start of a lifelong story. And the engagement ring you choose should capture both your emotion and your style.</p><p>At Lucira Jewelry, we believe each ring should hold the same reaction as your first “ yes”. From lab grown diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\" title=\"engagement rings\">engagement rings</a> that shine with purpose to minimalist engagement rings that whisper timeless beauty, each design captures a unique feeling of courage, joy, or connection that defines your love story. </p><p>In this blog, we have compiled 11 most elegant and simple Engagement Rings, each representing a different emotion in that unforgettable journey to “Yes”.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_kKqW7n": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Radiant Solitaire Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Radiant Solitaire Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": "understanding"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_gE3cJC": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1_51fe9578-8620-4231-94ff-940713ed520a.jpg",
            "text": "<p>The <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/products/1-50-ct-classic-radiant-solitaire-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"radiant solitaire\">radiant solitaire</a> is bold yet timeless, a perfect choice for those who appreciate clean lines and brilliance without excess. Its rectangular facets catch light beautifully, making it ideal for someone who wants modern elegance with a touch of individuality. </p><p>Say yes if you love the idea of a ring that stands through brilliance, not size.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BxFmqg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Round Cut Solitaire Engagement Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Round Cut Solitaire Engagement Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_AynJ8F": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_4eeb2d8a-aaae-4327-a64d-c9f95bbd72f7.jpg",
            "text": "<p>This is the most popular diamond engagement ring shape for a reason. Its symmetry and sparkle symbolize enduring love and perfection. Whether paired with platinum, yellow gold, white gold or rose gold, it adapts effortlessly to every era and outfit.</p><p>Say yes if you’re drawn to timeless beauty, the kind that never competes for attention but always feels right.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jbd43L": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Marquise & Emerald Toi et Moi",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Marquise & Emerald Toi et Moi</h2>",
            "custom_id": "Round"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zpxzBh": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Princess_-_The_Modern_Icon_02fb6bbe-fcc7-440d-bef0-bf2cf4baa660.jpg",
            "text": "<p>‘You and Me’ - The ‘Toi et Moi’ ring celebrates two distinct stones side by side, symbolising the union of two souls. The marquise stone adds vintage drama, while the emerald cut adds refined sophistication. Together they represent the essence of modern love. If your love story is the story of opposites attract, if you are the yin to their yang, and complement each other, this design is for you. </p><p>Say yes if you appreciate artistry and symbolism. This custom diamond engagement ring is for those who value meaning as much as beauty<br/><br/></p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ejh96n": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Elegance Trilogy Diamond Ring ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Elegance Trilogy Diamond Ring </h2>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_VWDmRU": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4_1c5c2735-0846-4fad-b11a-1918b360536b.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A trilogy ring features three diamonds:  your past, your present, and your future. This design embodies the commitment that grows stronger with time. Each stone compliments the other, symbolizing how two lives intertwine and evolve together. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BWVmEe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Elegance Ring Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Say yes if you’re drawn to sentimental designs that carry emotional depth. This elegant engagement ring is the perfect for someone who cherishes every moment.</p><p>Go the extra step by customising this ring with engravings that carry a personal message to embark on the journey of forever with a ring that sparkles for a lifetime. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bPLMNC": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Classic Solitaire Emerald Ring ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Classic Solitaire Emerald Ring </h2>",
            "custom_id": "cushion"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zwVAkV": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/5_bc3071d3-6f47-4612-982f-1764329bedca.jpg",
            "text": "<p>The emerald cut is for the woman who values composure and class. Its long, open facets and mirror-like effects bring a sense of calm elegance, nothing flashy, just refined confidence. It’s favorite among brides with modern yet minimalist aesthetics.<br/>Say yes if you admire subtlety and structure.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_TbC4mN": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Classic Solitaire Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p> This diamond engagement ring proves that elegance isn't about excess, it's about precision, clarity and quiet beauty</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_dEkM3m": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Pear Shaped Halo",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Pear Shaped Halo</h2>",
            "custom_id": "emerald"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NwRy9R": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/6_fa23b6a8-0c9e-44e9-b389-07d401e75011.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A teardrop shaped diamond encircled by a halo of smaller stones. This ring elongates the finger and sparkles from every angle, blending vintage charm with modern brilliance.</p><p>Say yes if you love designs that are soft yet striking. This modern engagement ring bridges classic romance with contemporary charm.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jMYfry": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Solitaire Heart Shape Diamond Engagement Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Solitaire Heart Shape Diamond Engagement Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_iiFrKE": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/7_8912f9a5-5de4-4b6e-92bc-9f662ef18fcb.jpg",
            "text": "<p>The heart shaped diamond engagement ring is the ultimate symbol of love, playful yet deeply personal. A piece that stands out in both meaning and shape. It's perfect for someone sentimental, who believes love should be felt and shown.</p><p>Say yes if your love story deserves a symbol as expressive as your heart.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CbXLkg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Emerald and Round Diamond Toi Et Moi Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Emerald and Round Diamond Toi Et Moi Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": "marquise"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NiGrXL": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/8_0f175032-32be-4047-94c3-0033e77bf139.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Our modern Toi et Moi pairs emerald and round cuts to create a design full of motion and symmetry. The two stones face each other, representing equality and partnership. This modern engagement ring feels modern but classic, a refreshing option for contemporary couples.<br/>Say yes if your relationship is built on balance and mutual admiration. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_hEAXhx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Pear Diamond Trilogy Engagement Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Pear Diamond Trilogy Engagement Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NN3FF4": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/9_41337834-d136-49b2-87aa-95316df739e4.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Three pear shaped diamonds come together to create a design that's soft and dynamic. It is modern yet sentimental, and its fluid shape adds movement to sparkle. It is a beautiful option for someone who believes love keeps growing through every stage and season. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cTfgNx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Pear Diamond Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Say yes if you’re drawn to rare ring designs that carry deeper meaning and stand out  with sophistication.</p>",
            "custom_id": "hexa"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BfYxxj": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Round Solitaire With Diamond Accented Split Shank Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Round Solitaire With Diamond Accented Split Shank Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_WhjVYq": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/10_262d448f-da8f-455a-95e4-b0ef5bfcb7fb.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A delicate twist on a classic, the split shank design adds depth and balance while keeping the silhouette clean. The side detailing catches light beautifully like a small touch to its character. Its elegant enough for everyday wear yet special enough for a lifetime.</p><p>Say yes if you love intricate designs that symbolise how your meant-to-be story unfolded over time. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jGPUrV": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": " Princess Cut Solitaire Engagement Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2> Princess Cut Solitaire Engagement Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_7bhRtt": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/11.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Geometric, sharp, and endlessly radiant, this princess cut is the modern bride’s statement. It’s edges sparkle with precision, giving it a sleek, architectural appeal.</p><p>It’s perfect for those who love clarity and confidence in design <br/>Say yes if you want a ring that feels powerful yet feminine, a ring that moves with poise in every gesture.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ND9GCy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lab Grown Diamond Rings: A Modern Revolution",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Lab Grown Diamond Rings: A Modern Revolution</h2><p>Every generation redefines what love and luxury mean. For today’s couples, its no longer just about sparkle, its about significance and that's where lab grown diamonds change the story. They offer the same beauty, brilliance and durability as mined diamonds but with a smaller environmental footprint.</p><p>They make it possible to invest in higher clarity or larger carat, all while choosing sustainably. </p><p>Say yes to diamonds that shine not only brighter, but truer, inside and out.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cPbJNJ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Custom Designs",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Custom Designs</h2><p>When love doesn't fit a mold, neither should your ring. That's why Lucira’s bespoke design experience begins with your story. Every detail, from the curve of the band to the way light hits your diamond, becomes a reflection of you. Maybe it's a hidden engraving that only you two know about. Maybe it's a diamond color inspired by the first city you travelled to together, a soft curve that mirrors the bridge of Paris or warm gold tone that reminds you of sunsets of Santorini. Or maybe its a design that feels nothing like what you’ve seen before because love in your world looks a little different.</p><p>At Lucira, our artisans turn emotions into form, sketch by sketch, setting by setting. Because the most meaningful rings are not just worn, they’re lived in.</p><p>So if your love deserves something that feels deeply, unmistakably yours, create with us.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3fBN74": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion - The Final Lucira Tip",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion: Your Yes, Your forever </h2><p>Choosing an engagement ring is both emotional and practical, a mix of instinct and intention. The right one won't just look beautiful; it will feel like home.</p><p>Whether it's the confidence of the radiant solitaire, the modern geometry of the princess cut or the tenderness of the heart shaped ring, each piece in Lucira Jewelry’s collection is designed to capture one thing, that perfect unforgettable yes.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion"
          }
        }
      },
